    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Headlong Hunt is a puzzle game about guiding a skittish animal. Capture it by using simple interactions in surprisingly deep and satisfying ways - be two steps ahead as you choose to hide from sight or send the creature bolting. Think forwards and backwards to set up the perfect path to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/a7787b15b95963ada05761468b1990a9.poster.avif?t=1757946449\" width=510 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/a7787b15b95963ada05761468b1990a9.webm?t=1757946449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/a7787b15b95963ada05761468b1990a9.mp4?t=1757946449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/692a4d844564e381deef2a858654c65f.poster.avif?t=1757946449\" width=510 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/692a4d844564e381deef2a858654c65f.webm?t=1757946449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2323660/extras/692a4d844564e381deef2a858654c65f.mp4?t=1757946449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Over 100 expertly-crafted puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Elegant mechanics which elaborate on the central theme and interact in surprising ways </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A seamless overworld map, with two main paths and optional islands</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique painterly art style and atmospheric original soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Smooth controls including undo and undo through reset</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Full controller support and control rebinding</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
